{{Top|leg}}
The '''Trade Federation ore barge''' was a narrow ship that had been used by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] for centuries prior to [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]]. [[Viceroy of the Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation Viceroy]] [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Nute Gunray]] believed it to be the basis for the [[C-9979 landing craft/Legends|C-9979 landing craft]] designed by [[Haor Chall Engineering/Legends|Haor Chall Engineering]], with the fuselage instead set on a pedestal and capped with two enormous wings.

